Introduction
Here is a list of web sites of EUnet customers. As many of them have leased lines and run their own web server, this list is not complete. If I missed some (I'm sure, I did) please notify your favourite webmaster. You may also have a look at one of the compilations of information systems in Austria. There are quite a few out there.

This is a KWICed (keyword in context) index. The lights have the following meanings:

site is fully operational
site operational, came online recently or had complete rehaul
site is under maintenance
site is under construction
site status is (yet) unknown
The idea is that our customers have full control over this status display using their site administration facility.
